44 …."
45 SECTION 1.(c) The Dean of the School of Health Sciences at Winston-Salem State
46 University shall establish initial selection criteria for recipients no later than November 15, 2025,
47 and shall make available applications to prospective students no later than December 31, 2025.
48 SECTION 1.(d) The Dean of the School of Health Sciences at Winston-Salem State
49 University shall select recipients and award the initial forgivable loans for the 2026-2027
50 academic year no later than April 1, 2026.
