1 SECTION 1.(e) There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Nursing Fellows
2 Program Trust Fund for the 2025-2026 fiscal year the sum of one million four hundred thousand
3 dollars ($1,400,000) in recurring funds to establish the Nursing Fellows Program described in
4 this section.
5 SECTION 1.(f) This section applies beginning with applications for enrollment in
6 the Nursing Fellows Program in the 2026-2027 academic year.
7
8 PART II. FUNDS FOR CURRICULUM SUPPORT FOR NURSING STUDENTS AT
9 WINSTON-SALEM STATE UNIVERSITY
10 SECTION 2. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Board of Governors
11 of The University of North Carolina the sum of one hundred thousand dollars ($100,000) in
12 recurring funds for the 2025-2026 fiscal year to be allocated to Winston-Salem State University
13 (WSSU) to provide mentoring, coaching, and other curriculum-support services for students
14 enrolled in a nursing degree program at WSSU.
15
16 PART III. EFFECTIVE DATE
17 SECTION 3. This act becomes effective July 1, 2025.
